      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that even when i try to \"reach out,\" it feels like more work. more people and their expectations and their pity. it's all just more noise. i feel like i've run out of ways to fix this. everything i do just makes the hole deeper. i feel like i'm just a ghost in this lab already, just going through the motions of a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore. i don't want to \"reach out,\" i just want the silence.",
